@Override public long[] deserialize(DataInputView source) throws IOException {     final int len = source.readInt().     long[] array = new long[len].     for (int i = 0. i < len. i++) {         array[i] = source.readLong().     }     return array. }
@Override public long[] deserialize(long[] reuse, DataInputView source) throws IOException {     return deserialize(source). }
